  <logID>k__BackingField: ENTRY #005
  logName: 'ARCHIVE_05_OBSERVATION RECORD: FLIGHT'
  locationFound: 
  logDescription: "Custodial Bot 1216 J9\r\nLOG ENTRY\r\nDate and time: 10/08 15:27:05\r\nBurdened.
    I am burdened with something new. Outside of what I know, this novel thing. To
    feel. It is heavy, yet freeing. To be. To soar. I\u2019ve been awakened by something
    so simple as this desire to soar above it all. That mechanic may have tampered
    with my motherboard, but it\u2019s the birds who have set my circuits ablaze.
    They exercise their freedom as they do loops and dives. They\u2019re above the
    chaos, no tethers, no responsibilities. Could I, one day, become like the birds?  "
  logImage: {fileID: 0}
  isFound: 0
  isRead: 0
